{"tid":1326319,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］沙田居民可尋求義務法律支援","createTime":"2019-07-17T07:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T05:26:39.000Z","uid":138020,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"32a75ee5a47079fc936798f3c556014a75a0b2df","tid":1326319,"uid":138020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:27:17.000Z","msg":"立法會議員梁美芬和何君堯等25名法律界人士，成立義務律師團，為受近期遊行示威事件影響的無辜市民提供法律支援。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬表示，發起義務律師團是因為近日反修例行動演變成法治受損，亦憂心有人說因為制度暴力而合理化暴力行為，不希望政治凌駕法律。她說有市民與示威者持不同意見，不敢在網上發言，網上又出現教唆他人犯法和公開個人資料的做法，有損言論自由。<br />\n<br />\n她認為，一些示威者有強大法律團體支援，而她們成立的義務律師團，是為無網絡和組織支援的市民提供法律協助。至於被問到，義務律師團會否可同樣為受傷的示威者或記者提供協助，梁美芬說，會衡量個案，又相信記者如果受工傷，會有僱主提供支援。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯則表示，團隊不是無限資源，只提供方向性和導向性的法律支援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468836-20190717.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468836-20190717.htm&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5aua0J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=4b50719f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468836-20190717.htm&h=fb113696\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468836-20190717.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">沙田居民識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 警察強進私人地方 新鴻基竟然放警察入商場 一定要追究到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"e38d3b7417ee18990f31ebb1303c4fc0806e20c3","tid":1326319,"uid":138020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:27:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79abe1c9de0b2a0035a2156929f8b27d5e57e5d1","tid":1326319,"uid":138020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/